vu?

00:12:33.266 --> 00:12:35.400
in ⟨DETROIT⟩.

00:12:37.952 --> 00:12:43.040
deys iz a bar-mitsve fun mayn shvester's zun,

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:44.656
fun an eynikl,

00:12:44.656 --> 00:12:49.303
in eyn toyznt nayn hundert nayntsiker yor, befor zi iz geshtorbn.

00:12:50.625 --> 00:12:55.570
dort iz UNK Meyerko,

00:12:56.076 --> 00:12:59.968
Borekh, der zun, Volvi,

00:13:00.767 --> 00:13:02.685
Zalmi, der zun,

00:13:04.277 --> 00:13:07.020
an eynikl, Gitele,

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:11.870
 Yoli, di sh- a shnur,

00:13:12.006 --> 00:13:13.654
Anye, a shnur,

00:13:14.065 --> 00:13:17.062
Piri, a shnur, Mendl, der zun,

00:13:20.595 --> 00:13:24.140
UNK, MIKEY, dos eynikl,

00:13:25.422 --> 00:13:27.154
Malkele...

00:13:27.784 --> 00:13:30.060
di ze ikh nisht...

00:13:31.294 --> 00:13:32.435
un ikh.

00:13:33.555 --> 00:13:34.278
vu?

00:13:34.750 --> 00:13:37.180
 in Bruklin.
